  <brief_title>Treatment of Patients With Nocturia</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase III Randomized, Double Blind, Placebo Control, Multicenter Study to Investigate the Efficacy and Safety of SER120 Nasal Spray Formulation in Patients With Nocturia</official_title>
